E banners~
The banners bear the crest of Kel'Shadra - a void eye ringed by
seven black stars. The fabric is impossibly cold to the touch and
seems to absorb light rather than merely blocking it.
~
S

#613
The Eastern Alcove~
A small alcove has been carved into the eastern wall of the courtyard.
Within it stands a stone pedestal bearing a strange puzzle device: a set
of interlocking obsidian rings that can be rotated independently. Each
ring bears a symbol. Someone has been here recently - fresh scratches
mark the pedestal where impatient hands tried to force the mechanism.
~
