E puzzle pedestal rings~
The three obsidian rings can each be rotated. If you study the symbols
carefully, you notice that each ring depicts phases of some celestial body.
The correct sequence will unlock a hidden door. Type 'solve puzzle' to
attempt to align the rings. (Hint: full, crescent, new)
~
S

#614
The Hidden Vault~
A narrow chamber revealed by the correct manipulation of the eastern
puzzle. The walls are lined with obsidian shelves bearing ancient
tomes and strange artifacts. A faint glow emanates from a gem embedded
in the far wall. Most of the tomes are too damaged to read, but the
presence of wealth is undeniable.
~
