#616
The Hall of Broken Thrones~
Three massive thrones of black stone have been overturned and shattered
in this chamber. The walls bear the scars of ancient battle - sword and
spell marks that must be centuries old. In the rubble between the thrones,
dark energy pulses fitfully, the remnant of whatever cataclysm destroyed
this room. The ceiling has partially collapsed on the western side.
