#619
The Chamber of Whispers~
Every sound made in this small chamber is amplified and reflected in strange
ways. Your own footsteps sound like the tread of armies. Your breathing
becomes a crowd of whispered words in a language you almost understand.
The walls are covered in thousands of scratched names - all in the same
writing style, as if carved by a single hand over a very, very long time.
~
