#621
The Gallery of Failures~
Lining the walls of this grim gallery are portrait frames - but the
paintings have been deliberately destroyed, leaving only scraps of canvas
and flecks of dark paint. Beneath each ruined portrait is a plaque bearing
a name and a date. The dates span centuries. Below the plaques, in smaller
text, each reads: 'Failed.' The gallery is very long.
~
