#622
The Frost Sanctum~
Cold beyond reason fills this chamber. Your breath hangs in clouds before
you and the floor is sheeted with black ice. In the center of the room,
a frozen figure stands within a block of void-ice - a tall humanoid whose
features are distorted by the freezing. It holds out one hand, and in that
hand is a key. The key is clearly visible through the ice but completely
inaccessible.
~
