tracking your movements. The key in its hand appears to be obsidian, deeply
carved with void runes. If you could thaw the ice without shattering the key...
The puzzle: the temperature runes on the walls suggest the ice responds to
heat runes arranged in the correct order. Examine the walls for guidance.
~
S

#623
The Labyrinth Entrance~
The passage here opens into the beginning of the famous Labyrinth of Lost
Voices - a maze of corridors built to confuse and disorient intruders. The
walls here are lined with mirrors of polished obsidian, but the reflections
in them don't quite match reality. Your reflection moves a fraction of a
second after you do, and sometimes appears to make gestures you didn't.
~
