#624
The Scorched Corridor~
A passage leading north from the armory of ashes. The walls here are
scorched in patterns that suggest tremendous heat was released in a single
instant - as if something exploded outward from the armory. The scorch
marks grow less severe as you move north, suggesting whatever happened
originated in the chamber to the south. Strange symbols are burned into
the ceiling overhead.
~
